@startuml sd_OperationLogService_log
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title OperationLogService.log(username, operation, detail, ip, success) - 操作日志记录

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "PayrollController" as Ctrl
participant "OperationLogService" as LogSvc
participant "OperationLogRepository" as LogRepo
participant "OperationLog\n(实体)" as LogEntity

Client -> Ctrl: POST /api/payroll/calculate\n{yearMonth, trialRun}
note right of Ctrl : 工资计算完成后\n调用日志服务
Ctrl -> LogSvc: log("admin", "工资计算",\n"2024年3月工资计算, 共50人",\n"192.168.1.1", true)
LogSvc -> LogEntity: OperationLog.builder()
note right of LogSvc #F0F8FF
  **构建日志实体:**
  username = "admin"
  operation = "工资计算"
  detail = "2024年3月工资..."
  ipAddress = "192.168.1.1"
  result = "SUCCESS"
  createTime = now()
end note
LogSvc -> LogRepo: save(logEntity)
LogRepo --> LogSvc: 持久化后的OperationLog
LogSvc --> Ctrl: void
Ctrl --> Client: ApiResponse(计算结果)
note right of Ctrl : 如果log失败\n不影响主业务事务

@enduml
